In [[2023]] I began drawing again, having previously quit around around the age
of 8 or 9. I enjoy it immensely and even if I'm not great at it I love putting
on an album and completely losing track of time . It's relaxing once you loosely
know what you are doing, and there are always so many things to study that
you'll never run out of interesting things to sketch.

Here are some things I have drawn. Even though I started in 2023 I drew
embarassingly little that year. It's my goal this year to draw more because
that's the only way I will ever get better. I'm also trying to draw faster (also
so I can output more) but that comes only with practice too.

